    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong data-start=\"4502\" data-end=\"4534\">Shrouded Glen — Caern Shroud</strong><br data-start=\"4534\" data-end=\"4537\" /><em data-start=\"4537\" data-end=\"4583\">Caern State (from Rite of the Shrouded Glen)</em></p><p data-start=\"4585\" data-end=\"4760\">Spirits of concealment, misdirection, and silence bind themselves to the Caern. Those who do not belong find the Caern difficult to remember, locate, or deliberately approach.</p><p data-start=\"4762\" data-end=\"4773\"><strong data-start=\"4762\" data-end=\"4773\">Effects</strong></p><ul data-start=\"4774\" data-end=\"5159\"><li data-start=\"4774\" data-end=\"4925\"><p data-start=\"4776\" data-end=\"4925\">Creatures attempting to locate, track, or deliberately travel to the Caern must succeed on a Wisdom (Survival) or Intelligence (Investigation) check.</p></li><li data-start=\"4926\" data-end=\"5065\"><p data-start=\"4928\" data-end=\"4965\">The DC is determined by Caern Rating:</p><ul data-start=\"4968\" data-end=\"5065\"><li data-start=\"4968\" data-end=\"4985\"><p data-start=\"4970\" data-end=\"4985\">Rating 1: DC 14</p></li><li data-start=\"4988\" data-end=\"5005\"><p data-start=\"4990\" data-end=\"5005\">Rating 2: DC 15</p></li><li data-start=\"5008\" data-end=\"5025\"><p data-start=\"5010\" data-end=\"5025\">Rating 3: DC 16</p></li><li data-start=\"5028\" data-end=\"5045\"><p data-start=\"5030\" data-end=\"5045\">Rating 4: DC 17</p></li><li data-start=\"5048\" data-end=\"5065\"><p data-start=\"5050\" data-end=\"5065\">Rating 5: DC 18</p></li></ul></li><li data-start=\"5066\" data-end=\"5109\"><p data-start=\"5068\" data-end=\"5109\">At Corruption 3+, the DC is reduced by 2.</p></li><li data-start=\"5110\" data-end=\"5159\"><p data-start=\"5112\" data-end=\"5159\">At Corruption 5, the shroud collapses entirely.</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"5161\" data-end=\"5294\"><strong data-start=\"5161\" data-end=\"5175\">Divination</strong><br />Magical effects used to locate, scry upon, or divine the Caern automatically fail unless they are 6th level or higher.</p><p data-start=\"5296\" data-end=\"5315\"><strong data-start=\"5296\" data-end=\"5315\">Who Is Affected</strong></p><ul data-start=\"5316\" data-end=\"5480\"><li data-start=\"5316\" data-end=\"5364\"><p data-start=\"5318\" data-end=\"5364\">Non-Garou and unrecognized Garou are affected.</p></li><li data-start=\"5365\" data-end=\"5416\"><p data-start=\"5367\" data-end=\"5416\">Recognized Garou and contributors are unaffected.</p></li><li data-start=\"5417\" data-end=\"5480\"><p data-start=\"5419\" data-end=\"5480\">Allies may bypass through escort or tokens (ST adjudication).</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"5482\" data-end=\"5497\"><strong data-start=\"5482\" data-end=\"5497\">Limitations</strong></p><ul data-start=\"5498\" data-end=\"5689\"><li data-start=\"5498\" data-end=\"5533\"><p data-start=\"5500\" data-end=\"5533\">Does not make the Caern invisible</p></li><li data-start=\"5534\" data-end=\"5568\"><p data-start=\"5536\" data-end=\"5568\">Does not stop assault once found</p></li><li data-start=\"5569\" data-end=\"5621\"><p data-start=\"5571\" data-end=\"5621\">Does not affect creatures already inside the Caern</p></li><li data-start=\"5622\" data-end=\"5689\"><p data-start=\"5624\" data-end=\"5689\">Cannot be selectively dismissed without performing the Rite again</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"5691\" data-end=\"5826\"><strong data-start=\"5691\" data-end=\"5715\">Tag (do not remove):</strong><br data-start=\"5715\" data-end=\"5718\" /><code data-start=\"5718\" data-end=\"5826\">[GAROU_CAERN_STATE] parent=shrouded-glen; effect=shroud; exclusiveGroup=shrouded-glen; duration=indefinite</code></p>",
      "chat": "<p><strong data-start=\"4502\" data-end=\"4534\">Shrouded Glen — Caern Shroud</strong><br data-start=\"4534\" data-end=\"4537\" /><em data-start=\"4537\" data-end=\"4583\">Caern State (from Rite of the Shrouded Glen)</em></p><p data-start=\"4585\" data-end=\"4760\">Spirits of concealment, misdirection, and silence bind themselves to the Caern. Those who do not belong find the Caern difficult to remember, locate, or deliberately approach.</p><p data-start=\"4762\" data-end=\"4773\"><strong data-start=\"4762\" data-end=\"4773\">Effects</strong></p><ul data-start=\"4774\" data-end=\"5159\"><li data-start=\"4774\" data-end=\"4925\"><p data-start=\"4776\" data-end=\"4925\">Creatures attempting to locate, track, or deliberately travel to the Caern must succeed on a Wisdom (Survival) or Intelligence (Investigation) check.</p></li><li data-start=\"4926\" data-end=\"5065\"><p data-start=\"4928\" data-end=\"4965\">The DC is determined by Caern Rating:</p><ul data-start=\"4968\" data-end=\"5065\"><li data-start=\"4968\" data-end=\"4985\"><p data-start=\"4970\" data-end=\"4985\">Rating 1: DC 14</p></li><li data-start=\"4988\" data-end=\"5005\"><p data-start=\"4990\" data-end=\"5005\">Rating 2: DC 15</p></li><li data-start=\"5008\" data-end=\"5025\"><p data-start=\"5010\" data-end=\"5025\">Rating 3: DC 16</p></li><li data-start=\"5028\" data-end=\"5045\"><p data-start=\"5030\" data-end=\"5045\">Rating 4: DC 17</p></li><li data-start=\"5048\" data-end=\"5065\"><p data-start=\"5050\" data-end=\"5065\">Rating 5: DC 18</p></li></ul></li><li data-start=\"5066\" data-end=\"5109\"><p data-start=\"5068\" data-end=\"5109\">At Corruption 3+, the DC is reduced by 2.</p></li><li data-start=\"5110\" data-end=\"5159\"><p data-start=\"5112\" data-end=\"5159\">At Corruption 5, the shroud collapses entirely.</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"5161\" data-end=\"5294\"><strong data-start=\"5161\" data-end=\"5175\">Divination</strong><br />Magical effects used to locate, scry upon, or divine the Caern automatically fail unless they are 6th level or higher.</p><p data-start=\"5296\" data-end=\"5315\"><strong data-start=\"5296\" data-end=\"5315\">Who Is Affected</strong></p><ul data-start=\"5316\" data-end=\"5480\"><li data-start=\"5316\" data-end=\"5364\"><p data-start=\"5318\" data-end=\"5364\">Non-Garou and unrecognized Garou are affected.</p></li><li data-start=\"5365\" data-end=\"5416\"><p data-start=\"5367\" data-end=\"5416\">Recognized Garou and contributors are unaffected.</p></li><li data-start=\"5417\" data-end=\"5480\"><p data-start=\"5419\" data-end=\"5480\">Allies may bypass through escort or tokens (ST adjudication).</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"5482\" data-end=\"5497\"><strong data-start=\"5482\" data-end=\"5497\">Limitations</strong></p><ul data-start=\"5498\" data-end=\"5689\"><li data-start=\"5498\" data-end=\"5533\"><p data-start=\"5500\" data-end=\"5533\">Does not make the Caern invisible</p></li><li data-start=\"5534\" data-end=\"5568\"><p data-start=\"5536\" data-end=\"5568\">Does not stop assault once found</p></li><li data-start=\"5569\" data-end=\"5621\"><p data-start=\"5571\" data-end=\"5621\">Does not affect creatures already inside the Caern</p></li><li data-start=\"5622\" data-end=\"5689\"><p data-start=\"5624\" data-end=\"5689\">Cannot be selectively dismissed without performing the Rite again</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"5691\" data-end=\"5826\"><strong data-start=\"5691\" data-end=\"5715\">Tag (do not remove):</strong><br data-start=\"5715\" data-end=\"5718\" /><code data-start=\"5718\" data-end=\"5826\">[GAROU_CAERN_STATE] parent=shrouded-glen; effect=shroud; exclusiveGroup=shrouded-glen; duration=indefinite</code></p>"
